<template>
    <headMenu :menu="menu"/>
</template>

<script scoped>
import headMenu from './headMenu.vue'
import { mapState } from 'vuex';
export default {
    components: {
        headMenu,
    },
    computed: {
        ...mapState({
            selectedCategory: state => state.selectedCategory
        })
    },
    data() {
        return {
            menu: '',
        };
    }
}
</script>
